      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "The shift in music represented here, while still maintaining the upbeat and lively nature, underscores the distinction between the two locations. By using this classical music, very much rooted in Western tradition, Sembène  effectively juxtaposes the two locations -- that of the westernized Plateau compared to the more traditional outskirts.",
        "format": "text/plain",
        "purpose": "commenting"
      },
      "target": {
