      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "How will they get food? 2 options: 1. Prostitution (culturally, not an option), thus option 2. Someone in the nearby community will most likely help feed them. Also, a reversal of stereotypical gender roles occurs here since Borom Sarret's wife must provide for the family.",
